members.member:

Creates a new meter operations that measures the rate at which the operation occurs.

Name of the meter.
Specifies what it is measuring, like the number of requests
The rate unit
The workspace Guid.
The correlation ID.
Custom Data to provide with the metric.
Any additional sinks to which this metric should be written to in addition to the defaults provided by the APM class.

/// 
See the example how to use

var meter = apm.MeterOperation(null, "MeterTest"," a simple meter test", "mark(s)");
DateTime now = DateTime.Now.AddSeconds(30);
while (DateTime.Now < now)
{
    Thread.Sleep(1000);
    meter.Mark();
}
meter.Write();

